name: codeGirl #4
description:
The fourth card in codeGirl story (edition of 5)

It’s a Spatial, Interactive work, pinned to IPFS
It responds to touch or gesture / IO

These StoryBlox are stand-alone but also link together to create a greater whole:
codeGirl is an interactive Visual Story that has won awards at the Tribeca Film Festival and London's Pixel Market. 
Here it has been completely reimagined for decentralized Web3 & I've recreated the assets in & for #VR.
